channel.description:
[center][img]http://i24.servimg.com/u/f24/16/54/01/96/sx11.jpg[/img][/center]
[center][img]http://i910.photobucket.com/albums/ac308/garfdore/intro.png[/img][/center] SmiteX is a Economic & pking server it has 474 & 525 gameframe (You can just click on the change button and it will change to 474 to 525) , i have always want SmiteX to grow to be a good & fun server . I am working on this project alone as i cant get any partners with me . I always dream to host my own private server & i finally did it today , i wanna show people that if you dream of something you wish to do or had , just go for it & you will fulfill your dreams its no lie as long as your willing too . SmiteX is a base from Wilderness Reloaded By crazyfazespy (I would like to thanks him for his base & a start for my coding experience) My goal is to have lots of players to play SmiteX & its all about the fun & making new friends , moparscape has been like my home & i like moarscape people when i needed help , they help me to get what i need . HAHAHA just a little introduction about myself & the server .
